|3 |    ├─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |
|4 |    │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY)|:EX10000|
|5 |    │   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |
|6 |    │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t1      |
|7 |    └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR      |        |
|8 |      └─TABLE GET                |tp1     |
